name: St. Mary's County Health Department
tweet: If you’re eligible for a booster dose, you may have questions about “mixing and matching.” CDC advises people to get the same booster as their initial vaccine, but allows people to “mix and match” if they have a different preference. Learn more:  https://t.co/eZzmPMDnRE  https://t.co/SoMUq6BtNG
